high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Take the knife out of the sink.
Walk over to the kitchen counter with the appliances on top.
Put the knife inside the black jar on the counter.
Pick up the jar from the counter.
Walk over to the table stand near the door.
Put the jar on top of the table stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a jar with a knife inside it on top of the black table stand.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the butter knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left towards the toaster.
Place the butter knife in the mug on the counter by the toaster.
Pick up the mug with the butter knife from the counter.
Turn right, walk towards the black table, turn right, then turn left and across the room to the black table.
Place the mug with the butter knife on the top of the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with the dirty knife on the black table

high_descs: Walk forward to the cabinets then shift slightly to the right so you are facing the wall with the sink at a forty five degree angle to your right.
Pick up the knife from in the sink.
Turn around and walk until you are even with the toaster and coffee maker then turn to face them.
Place the knife in the cup sitting near the toaster.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn around and walk a few steps then turn left walk to the wall and turn right and walk until the small black table with shelves is in front of you.
Place the cup with the knife in it to the right of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it on the table in the kitchen.

high_descs: Walk forward and face the counter next to the sink.
Grab the knife that is in the sink.
Turn left and walk and face the toaster with the cup in front of it.
Place the knife inside the cup.
Grab the cup off the counter.
Turn around and walk to the table in the corner of the room.
Place the cup next to the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the cup with the knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the sink then turn left.
Pick up the butter knife from the sink,
Turn left and take a step then turn left and walk to the coffee maker on you left and turn left to face it and take a step.
Put the knife in the cup in front of you.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn around and walk to the white table in front of you then turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the small black table.
Put the cup to the right of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward and face the sink to the right.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk forward and turn left to face the counter with the vase on it.
Put the knife in the vase on the counter.
Pick up the vase with the knife in it on the counter.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room and face the black table at the end of the counter.
Place the vase with a knife in it on the black table at the end of the counter.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a vase plus move it to the black table at the end of the counter.
